    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pale yellow, lemon-scented essential oil derived from the tropical lemongrass Cymbopogon nardus, native to South Asia. This oil is used in perfumes, soaps, and insect repellents.</Note_Text>
